 {"id":"mu-kex4","title":"t4c forward build: productize discovery prototype into crates/t4c","description":"Productize the validated t4c discovery prototype (scripts/t4c + t4c-notes.md report; design map agent memory f0e3a4fa) into a Rust crate crates/t4c in the mu workspace. LEAF crate: dep arrow mu->t4c only; builds standalone (cargo build -p t4c, zero sibling path-deps) so it works as an external library too. Model = registry-as-trait yielding a SHALLOW path-addressed tree (source.tool.subcommand, ~3 levels, then free args); transports are projections (CLI dotted-path + mu-native rpc). Surface tuned for a model consumer: find is the semantic FRONT DOOR returning {path, schema, suggested-call}; bare-prefix walk = terse one-line-per-node; meta-FLAGS --help-ai/--schema/--json (never path segments); forgiving fuzzy-fallback on path miss; JSON-first on all reads. Scope phases 1-3, STOP at the phase-3 human-validation gate (do NOT fake gpt-in-mu / cold-Claude dogfood). Branch t4c-forward-build, commit-only, no push. Worklist: br list --label goal:2026-05-29:SELF","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-05-29T06:53:38.827810192Z","created_by":"tcovert","updated_at":"2026-06-07T06:23:58.031418668Z","source_repo":"mu","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"comments":[{"id":68,"issue_id":"mu-kex4","author":"tcovert","text":"Sub-beads (goal:2026-05-29:mu-kex4):\n  mu-kex4.1 scaffold leaf crate         (root)\n  mu-kex4.2 registry-trait + path-tree  (blockedBy mu-kex4.1)\n  mu-kex4.3 CLI surface                 (blockedBy mu-kex4.2)\n  mu-kex4.4 discover                    (blockedBy mu-kex4.2)\n  mu-kex4.5 standard + templates        (blockedBy mu-kex4.3)\n  mu-kex4.6 mu-native + rpc [GATE]      (blockedBy mu-kex4.2,mu-kex4.3)\n  mu-kex4.7 report + data point         (blockedBy mu-kex4.5,mu-kex4.6)\nWorklist: br list --label goal:2026-05-29:mu-kex4","created_at":"2026-05-29T06:53:40Z"},{"id":70,"issue_id":"mu-kex4","author":"tcovert","text":"